reviewText: As a hardcore wrestling fan I loved this DVD... but Billy Jack Hayes... he can Suck It. That guy needs to get a grip on reality, he has NO clue what he is talking about and I think he just made a scene like that because people forgot about him. Good DVD -so sad that it happened and that because of it all one of the most talented wrestlers will never be reconized again because of something so selfish and sadistic on his part.
Didn't expect this to be a happy ending.  But reading/seeing the ins and outs of this tortured sole put a new perspective on his story.
Well I was expecting to see something about everything that I have never seen before about every thing that went down
